article.description: — Justin Webster had 16 points as Hawaii narrowly defeated Long Beach State 78-76 on Friday night.
article.headline: Webster scores 16 to carry Hawaii past Long Beach St. 78-76
article.linkText: Webster scores 16 to carry Hawaii past Long Beach St. 78-76
article.story: HONOLULU -- — Justin Webster had 16 points as Hawaii narrowly defeated Long Beach State 78-76 on Friday night. JoVon McClanahan had 13 points for Hawaii (9-8, 7-8 Big West Conference). Justin Hemsley added 12 points and seven rebounds. Mate Colina had 10 points. Chance Hunter scored a season-high 23 points and had nine rebounds for the Beach (5-8, 4-5). Isaiah Washington added 17 points. Jadon Jones had 12 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
